OL,3,CBridge linking England and Scotland
OL,4,Ccloses for maintenance
OL,6,FA historic suspension bridge linking
OL,7,FScotland and England has closed for
OL,8,Fmaintenance works.
OL,10,FThe Union Chain Bridge spans the River
OL,11,FTweed, linking Horncliffe in
OL,12,FNorthumberland with Fishwick in
OL,13,FBerwickshire.
OL,15,FThe bridge will be closed to all
OL,16,Ftraffic - including pedestrians and
OL,17,Fcyclists -until 26 July, though it is
OL,18,Fhoped that works will be concluded by
OL,19,Fthen.
