OL,3,CBridge linking England and Scotland
OL,4,Ccloses for maintenance
OL,6,FA full restoration of the 203-year-old
OL,7,Fbridge concluded in 2023, but
OL,8,Fcontractors are carrying out finishing
OL,9,Fworks which could not be completed at
OL,10,Fthe time.
OL,12,FThis includes work within the Scottish
OL,13,Fand English towers on the bridge and
OL,14,Freplacement work of some of the
OL,15,Fcarriageway deck panels.
