OL,3,CBridge linking England and Scotland
OL,4,Ccloses for maintenance
OL,6,FPaul Jones, director of environment
OL,7,Fand transport at Northumberland County
OL,8,FCouncil, said: "The restoration of the
OL,9,FUnion Chain Bridge was a hugely
OL,10,Fchallenging engineering scheme
OL,11,Fcombining the latest techniques along
OL,12,Fwith centuries-old craftsmanship and
OL,13,Fmaterials.
OL,15,F"While it was important to get the
OL,16,Fmain works completed and the bridge
OL,17,Fopen, there were some non-critical
OL,18,Felements which we need the contractor
OL,19,Fto complete, as well as some work to
OL,20,Freplace a number of the bridge deck
OL,21,Fpanels under warranty.
