OL,3,CBridge linking England and Scotland
OL,4,Ccloses for maintenance
OL,6,F"It's great to see the bridge being so
OL,7,Fwell used again, and we apologise for
OL,8,Fthe inconvenience, but we want the
OL,9,Fwork to be done while the weather is
OL,10,Fbetter and ahead of the main summer
OL,11,Fholiday season."
OL,13,FA diversion will be in place
OL,14,Fthroughout the closure period.
