OL,3,CBridge linking England and Scotland
OL,4,Ccloses for maintenance
OL,6,FThe restoration work on the bridge was
OL,7,Ffunded through #4.5 million received
OL,8,Ffrom the National Lottery Heritage
OL,9,FFund in September 2019, following a
OL,10,Fbid put together by Scottish Borders
OL,11,FCouncil and Northumberland County
OL,12,FCouncil, Museums Northumberland and
OL,13,Fcommunity group Friends of the Union
OL,14,FChain Bridge.
OL,16,FBoth councils committed match funding
OL,17,Ftowards the scheme, with other funds
OL,18,Fraised through work by the Friends of
OL,19,FUnion Chain Bridge, following concerns
OL,20,Fraised about the long-term future of
OL,21,Fthe structure.
